{'id': 13116020, 'body': "Hi, We are sorry to learn about what happened! Apple sends an email reminder a few days before the trial ends, but we can understand if you/your daughter missed it because the subject line does not specify the app name.  It sounds like you were referred to Apple Support for the refund because they handle billing for purchases via the App Store. However, if they decline your request when you call them, please let us know about it at support@breethe.com and we'll do our best to help you.

====

Thank you for working with us so we could provide an alternate solution for you. We appreciate your patience and understanding!", 'modified': '2020-01-25T17:21:50Z'}

{'id': 7157744, 'body': "Hi,

We're sorry to hear you feel this way towards our app. While it is true that it is not in our immediate plans to allow for the app's interface to turn when the device is turned in landscape view, this is very much something we'd like to add eventually. Unfortunately however, it will still take some time before we can easily add this feature. Please accept our apologies for any inconveniences this may cause you in the meantime.

Have a great day!", 'modified': '2019-02-05T01:01:36Z'}

